      "text": "Multi-Head Attention\n\nQ,K,V = Wq(x),Wk(x),Wv(x)  (B,S,E)\nReshape + Transpose          (B,H,S,Hd)\nScores = QK^T/sqrt(Hd)+mask  (B,H,S,S)\nContext = softmax(Scores)*V  (B,H,S,Hd)\nReshape + out_proj           (B,S,E)",
